graph TB
    subgraph "vLLM Spyre Container (odh-vllm-spyre-rhel9)"
        direction TB
        subgraph "Application Layer"
            TGISAdapter["vllm_tgis_adapter<br/>(Python entrypoint)"]
            VLLMEngine["vLLM Engine<br/>(Inference core)"]
            HTTPServer["HTTP API Server<br/>(uvicorn/FastAPI)<br/>Port 8000/TCP"]
            GRPCServer["gRPC Server<br/>(TGIS GenerationService)<br/>Port 8033/TCP"]
        end

        subgraph "Base Image Layer"
            RHAIIS["RHAIIS vllm-spyre-rhel9:3.2.2<br/>(UBI9 / Python / OpenSSL)"]
            SpyreDrivers["IBM Spyre Drivers"]
        end

        TGISAdapter -->|starts| HTTPServer
        TGISAdapter -->|starts| GRPCServer
        TGISAdapter -->|wraps| VLLMEngine
        VLLMEngine -->|uses| SpyreDrivers
        RHAIIS -->|provides| SpyreDrivers
        RHAIIS -->|provides| TGISAdapter
    end

    Client["Client / User<br/>(via KServe Router)"]
    KServeRouter["KServe Router"]
    ServingRuntime["ServingRuntime CR"]
    RhodsOperator["rhods-operator"]
    SpyreHW["IBM Spyre<br/>Hardware Accelerator"]
    ModelStorage["Model Storage<br/>(S3 / PVC / HF Hub)"]

    Client -->|inference request| KServeRouter
    KServeRouter -->|HTTP /v1/completions<br/>Port 8000| HTTPServer
    KServeRouter -->|gRPC GenerationService<br/>Port 8033| GRPCServer
    RhodsOperator -->|manages| ServingRuntime
    ServingRuntime -->|references image| RHAIIS
    VLLMEngine -->|offloads inference| SpyreHW
    VLLMEngine -->|loads model at startup| ModelStorage

    style TGISAdapter fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style VLLMEngine fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style HTTPServer fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style GRPCServer fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style RHAIIS fill:#6c5ce7,color:#fff
    style SpyreDrivers fill:#6c5ce7,color:#fff
    style SpyreHW fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style KServeRouter fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style ServingRuntime fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style RhodsOperator fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style ModelStorage fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Client fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
